diodes and a full line of bridge rectifiers surge provides top quality products to our customers our production facilities are all qs ts certified and meet the aecq standards for automotive requirements we are a green partner with many of our customers we are continuously introducing new products to the market staying in the forefront of technology surge is a global company with headquarters in new york and sales and stocking locations throughout north america and asia surge’s sales staff including our sales managers  customer service team and tech support department are of the highest caliber and are here to do everything we can to make your experience with surge a great one surge is focused on helping customers meet their needs leveraging  years of experience surge helps customers bring their products to market using the highest quality components with the most competitive economics to scale surge has established a network of excellent independent sales representatives throughout north america promoting our products to their local customers additionally surge is franchised with  of the top distributors for these products avnet inc future electronics and tti inc these distributors open sales channels to their customers for surge’s products surge supplies its top quality products to customers in many market segments including power energy automotive computer telecom security as well as others for more information about surge or our products please contact our local sales representative in your area your local distributor sales branch or surge directly as a one stop shop surge looks forward to being your supply chain partner providing our competitive advantages and thanks you for choosing surge     home  recent news  investor relations  faq  contact  facebook   surge components  privacy policy investor relations home about us products news new products  featured products faq corporate quality certifications environmentalrohs packaging technical support contact us at 